Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一分一秒都不能等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,茱蒂，贾维斯叔叔他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,贾维斯叔叔他一定爱着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
